      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. so it's basically just the sugar and protein reacting cause of the heat. you mentioned it's like \"magic\" though... is there anything else that can mess with the reaction or stop the browning from happening? like if the pH is off or something?",
      "source": "evaluator"
